  "description": "A stunning sunset view featuring a silhouetted mountain range against a dramatically colorful sky. The sky is layered with vibrant hues of red, orange, and yellow, transitioning from a fiery glow near the horizon to deep, stormy-looking clouds above. The clouds are textured and almost appear as brushstrokes across the canvas of the sky. The mountain range provides a dark, contrasting base to the bright, colorful spectacle above. The horizon line is crisp and clear, creating a strong separation between the land and sky.",
